category: Libs
requires: cygwin libboost1.48 libgcc1 libstdc++6
external-source: beanstalkpp
sdesc: "C++ client library for beanstalk (runtime)"
ldesc: "Beanstalk++ is a client library for the beanstalk protocol, based upon
boost.

The library is not feature complete yet, but the most commonly used
functionality exists (putting and reserving jobs and so on). Functionality
which exists in the library should be considered stable, as it's used heavily
in production environment."
